message.body: Will you be buying me my birfday drank at moto I tonight? :)
Yea! Is there a keyboard btw?
You'll have to ask JT I'm not sure.
What time are you going to be there?
So I've had a series of not so great nights and as a result had some monster anxiety attacks... I feel bad though bc I'm always flaking on you.
Oh no! What's going on hunny?

Stress about stuff with Katie and how things are going to work out and feeling like I'm a bad person. Im just trying to make sense of it without giving happiness up but I'm still hurting people. I'm ok just feeling bad about not seeing you
Oh yeah I totally understand! Ill always be ready for a drink another time when we're both up for it! You know I love you. And I'm always here for you!!!
